# Memory

- Collection name: **`content_performance`** via `memory/chroma_client.py`.
- Embedding model pinned to **`text-embedding-3-small`** (OpenAI embedding function).
- CSV ingest columns: **`content_id`, `likes`, `shares`, `comments`** (`memory/update.py`). Delta uses `tools.scorer_rubric.engagement_index`.
